<h3 id="Input-Radio">Radio button Input</h3>

<p>        
    In order to render an input of type radio you will need to use the 
    <code>@@Html.BsInputFor</code> helper extension and 
    decorate your model property with <code>[BsControl(BsControlType.RadioButton)]</code>.
</p>

<p>
    To achieve the same behavior without the <code>BsControlAttribute</code>, you can use the specialized helpers:
    <code>BsRadioButtonFor</code> and <code>BsRadioButton</code>.
</p>

